OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start, a fine
OL,6,Fbut windy day is expected. Staying
OL,7,Fdry, however high cloud will limit the
OL,8,Fextent of any brighter or hazy sunny
OL,9,Fspells, Feeling warm, especially out
OL,10,Fthe wind, but cooler in any onshore
OL,11,Fbreeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud will break at times,
OL,14,Fgiving some clearer spells and
OL,15,Fallowing for temperatures to fall.
OL,16,FWith winds easing, the odd patch of
OL,17,Ffrost and very isolated valley fog is
OL,18,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,165,160,301,260,100,100
