OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day
OL,6,Fwith variable cloud. With lighter
OL,7,Fwinds and more frequent sunny spells,
OL,8,Fit will be feeling warmer than on
OL,9,FTuesday.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FCooler Thursday, with showery
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, clearing overnight
OL,14,Fwith frost possible. Likely staying
OL,15,Fdry Friday with variable cloud and
OL,16,Fsunny spells, but also windy. Further
OL,17,Frain spreading east Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
